# Ignorar arquivos C e C++
*.c linguist-vendored
*.h linguist-vendored
*.cpp linguist-vendored
*.cc linguist-vendored
*.cxx linguist-vendored
*.hpp linguist-vendored
*.hh linguist-vendored
*.hxx linguist-vendored

# Ignorar arquivos Makefile
Makefile linguist-vendored
*.mak linguist-vendored
*.mk linguist-vendored
*.cmake linguist-vendored
*.CMakeLists.txt linguist-vendored

# Ignorar arquivos Roff
*.1 linguist-vendored
