*.3 linguist-vendored
*.4 linguist-vendored
*.5 linguist-vendored
*.6 linguist-vendored
*.7 linguist-vendored
*.8 linguist-vendored
*.9 linguist-vendored
*.man linguist-vendored
*.roff linguist-vendored

# Ignorar arquivos CMaker (geralmente *.cmake e CMakeLists.txt já cobertos acima, mas só para garantir)
*.cmake linguist-vendored
